---
// src/components/Benefits.astro
import Image from "astro/components/Image.astro";

import cyborg from "../assets/cybord.png";
---

<section class="benefits">
  <!-- Background mountain silhouette (same as before) -->
  <svg class="mountains" viewBox="0 0 1920 400" preserveAspectRatio="none">
    <path
      d="M0,400 L0,200 L180,280 L360,150 L540,320 L720,100 L900,250 L1080,180 L1260,300 L1440,120 L1620,260 L1800,160 L1920,280 L1920,400 Z"
      fill="#0f2027"></path>
  </svg>

  <!-- Central hero image -->
  <div class="hero-image">
    <Image src={cyborg} alt="Bored Shinigamiz Hero" loading="eager" />
  </div>

  <div class="container">
    <!-- Title -->
    <header class="section-header">
      <h1>BENEFITS & UTILITIES</h1>
      <p>
        When you buy a Bored Shinigamiz, you're not simply buying a simple NFT,
        you're getting access to a community where benefits and utilities will
        increase with the time.
      </p>
    </header>

    <!-- Benefit Items with dotted lines -->
    <div class="benefits-grid">
      <!-- Top Left -->
      <div class="benefit top-left">
        <div class="icon">
          <div class="icon-bg"></div>
          <span class="label">NFT</span>
        </div>
        <h3>INCREASE THE VALUE OF YOUR NFT</h3>
        <p>
          If you are lucky and mint one of our rare BORED SHINIGAMIZ you can 5x,
          10x even x20 (maybe more) the value of your investment within a few
          days of holding it.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Top Right -->
      <div class="benefit top-right">
        <div class="icon">
          <div class="icon-bg"></div>
          <span class="label">BBB</span>
        </div>
        <h3>SHINIGAMIZ WILL TAKEOVER VALUE OF YOUR NFT</h3>
        <p>
          The quality of our design, our strong community, and our big campaign
          of marketing will bring a lot of demand and eyes on the project.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Bottom Left -->
      <div class="benefit bottom-left">
        <div class="icon vip">
          <div class="icon-bg"></div>
          <span class="label">VIP</span>
        </div>
        <h3>ACCESS TO VIP PRIVILEGES</h3>
        <p>
          Same as Bored Bunny, Bored Shinigamiz will have many benefits for
          future drop and collaborations we make. By holding a BBB, we want to
          reward you with privileges that will give you access to many benefits
          in the NFT space. Bored Bunny will keep growing with new projects that
          we plan to release.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .benefits {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 120vh;
    background: linear-gradient(
      to bottom,
      #0a171e 0%,
      #0f2027 50%,
      #112e3a 100%
    );
    color: white;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 120px 40px;
  }

  .mountains {
    position: absolute;
    bottom: 0;
    left: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 400px;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .hero-image {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    width: 720px;
    z-index: 2;
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .hero-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    filter: drop-shadow(0 30px 80px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9));
  }

  .container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 3;
    max-width: 1400px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 100px;
  }

  .section-header h1 {
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 8vw, 6rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, #e0f2fe, #7fecff);
    -webkit-background-clip: text;
    -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
    margin: 0 0 20px;
  }

  .section-header p {
    font-size: 1.3rem;
    color: #b0e0ff;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .benefits-grid {
    position: relative;
  }

  .benefit {
    position: absolute;
    max-width: 420px;
    background: rgba(15, 32, 39, 0.6);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    padding: 28px;
    border-radius: 20px;
    border: 1px solid rgba(127, 236, 255, 0.2);
  }

  .benefit h3 {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    margin: 16px 0;
    color: #7fecff;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 1px;
  }

  .benefit p {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: #b0e0ff;
  }

  .icon {
    width: 80px;
    height: 80px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: rgba(127, 236, 255, 0.15);
    border: 3px solid #7fecff;
    display: grid;
    place-items: center;
    position: relative;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
  }

  .icon-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 8px;
    background: radial-gradient(circle, #7fecff, transparent);
    border-radius: 50%;
    opacity: 0.3;
  }

  .label {
    font-weight: bold;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
    color: #0f2027;
    text-shadow: 0 0 10px #7fecff;
  }

  .vip .icon {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #7fecff, #00c3ff);
  }

  /* Position each benefit + dotted lines */
  .top-left {
    top: 10%;
    left: 5%;
  }
  .top-right {
    top: 8%;
    right: 5%;
  }
  .bottom-left {
    bottom: 15%;
    left: 8%;
  }

  /* Dotted connecting lines */
  .benefit::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute;
    border: 2px dotted #7fecff;
    opacity: 0.4;
  }

  .top-left::before {
    top: 60px;
    right: -180px;
    width: 200px;
    border-left: none;
    border-top: none;
  }
  .top-right::before {
    top: 60px;
    left: -180px;
    width: 200px;
    border-right: none;
    border-top: none;
  }
  .bottom-left::before {
    top: -80px;
    right: -120px;
    height: 160px;
    border-left: none;
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  @media (max-width: 1200px) {
    .benefit {
      position: static;
      max-width: 100%;
      margin: 40px auto;
    }
    .benefit::before {
      display: none;
    }
    .hero-image {
      width: 500px;
    }
  }
</style>
